ass=\"pl-c1\">2</span>);\n\n<span class=\"pl-c1\">console</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">log</span>(<span class=\"pl-smi\">v1</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">length</span>()); <span class=\"pl-c\">// 5 (magnitude)</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">normalized</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">v1</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">normalize</span>(); <span class=\"pl-c\">// Unit vector</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">sum</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">v1</span>.<span class=\"pl-c1\">add</span>(<span class=\"pl-smi\">v2</span>); <span class=\"pl-c\">// Vector addition</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">scaled</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">v1</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">multiply</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">2</span>); <span class=\"pl-c\">// Scalar multiplication</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Example:</h5><pre><code class=\"language-ts\"><span class=\"pl-c\">// Vector angle calculation</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">v1</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">Vector</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span>, <span class=\"pl-c1\">0</span>); <span class=\"pl-c\">// Points right</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">v2</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">new</span> <span class=\"pl-en\">Vector</span>(<span class=\"pl-c1\">0</span>, <span class=\"pl-c1\">1</span>); <span class=\"pl-c\">// Points up</span>\n<span class=\"pl-k\">const</span> <span class=\"pl-c1\">angle</span> <span class=\"pl-k\">=</span> <span class=\"pl-smi\">v1</span>.<span class=\"pl-en\">angle</span>(<span class=\"pl-smi\">v2</span>); <span class=\"pl-c\">// 90 degrees</span>\n</code></pre>\n<h5>Since:</h5><p>1.0.0</p>\n"},"parentId":1558,"hierarchy":[{"name":"Vector","isTarget":true,"linkId":"2606"}]}
